CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 13, 1952, pg. 27 reads: "Golfdom's Best - Being average wasn't good enough at the South Park golf course last week as the above champions proved in annexing UGA crowns...Gordon Goodson, next photo, came through brilliantly to best the Men's Amateur field...- Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gordon Goodson wearing plaid hat with brim, squatting with golf club in right hand and golf ball in front of him, on South Park golf course for UGA tournament
